				<td colspan="2"><span>Ok, if you are primarily a supporter, IE you depend on your songs alot, be it chant-kiting, aoe kiting or grouped, get IM3 and SM2 at least fi will be PPrst and foremost. IM3 is more important then SM3 due to the fact that &lt;1&gt; There are many more insrument mod songs then singing mod songs, and &lt;2&gt; there are easily attainable singign mod items &lt;VotS&gt;. After that, CA3/LR5, HA5, CS3/ID5, MC2. If you are close to your max stats before buffs, and maxed after buffs, go for planar power, if not, then it wont do you any good till you improve your gear. If you solo alot, IM is your highest priority, since it will make your new aas come faster and easier. Since you have FM, MC2 is a good investment to make, it helps alot with mana regen and is definitely worth it. If you look at my magelo, you notice Im missing some, but my own plan for the future is SM3, IIM, ISM. Then after that will be PP.</span></td>
