				<td colspan="2"><span>The three things that matter most in supporting a main tank are AC, Resists, and Charisma (for divine intervention) at least when you start seeing high-end bosses.  Interestingly, all 3 of the songs that boost those are singing based.  Do not neglect Singing Mastery because &quot;we don't have that many singing-based songs.&quot;  The ones that matter when you're tanking Rallos Zek or Mith Marr DO rely on your SM bonus.  
<br />

<br />
I have been recommending this a bit lately because I consider it an AA bargain -- Improved Natural Metabolism.  For a measly 3 AAs you can make those expensive stat foods last 50% longer.</span></td>
